                <h3>TEXT ALERTS / TEXT MESSAGING</h3>
                <p>You may sign up to receive text message alerts about your order placed on The Sites or through the mobile application or via Text Message Ordering. Please note that standard data and message rates may apply for text message alerts. Please contact your mobile phone carrier for details.</p>
                <h4>How to Sign Up </h4>
                <p>To sign up to receive text message alerts, you will need to provide your consent to opt-in for text message alerts on [domain name], after you have submitted your order. By opting-in to receive text alerts, you consent to receive up to two (2) text messages in a two (2) hour window of time, as of the time of sign-up. This opt-in only applies for two (2) text messages related to one (1) specific order. You will have to opt-in each time you place an order if you want to receive text message alerts for that order.</p>
                <p>When utilizing the Text Message Ordering service You may receive up to 2 text messages for each text message you send to the service.</p>
